textAnnotations.description:
HOLLYWOOD WRITERS WENT
ON STRIKE MONDAY, FORCING
LATE-NIGHT TALK SHOWS TO
AIR RERUNS. THE INDUSTRY
EXPECTS LONG STANDOFFS
IDON'T CARE IF IT'S
AN OLD LENO. FOR THE
LAST TIME, NOT
TONIGHT, I HAVE
A HEADACHE!”
